# Imports and Barrels

- Prefer path aliases for cross-feature/core/shared/api imports.
- Prefer public entry points (`index.ts`) over deep internal paths.
- Avoid long relative traversals like `../../../../`.
- Export feature public API from `src/app/features/<feature>/index.ts`.
- Keep barrel exports explicit to avoid leaking private internals.

## Intent

Use aliases and barrels to keep refactors local and imports readable.
